# {{projectName}}

DARE-shaped Laravel 11 API. Layered Design (Controller → Service → Repository → Model).

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
composer install
php artisan key:generate
docker compose up -d postgres
php artisan migrate --seed
php artisan l5-swagger:generate
php artisan serve
```

## Endpoints

- `POST /api/auth/login` — exchange email/password for Sanctum token
- `GET /api/auth/me` — current user (Bearer)
- `GET /api/users` — list users (paginated)
- `POST /api/users` — create user (admin only)
- `GET /openapi.json` — OpenAPI 3.x surface
- `GET /api/documentation` — Swagger UI (l5-swagger)

## Commands

- `php artisan serve` — dev server (port 8000)
- `php artisan pail` — tail logs
- `pest` (or `php artisan test`) — run tests
- `vendor/bin/phpstan analyse` — static analysis
- `composer audit` — dependency audit

